449
00:24:47,562 --> 00:24:48,592
Table 12.

450
00:24:50,162 --> 00:24:51,902
This is on the house.

451
00:24:52,802 --> 00:24:53,802
Thank you.

452
00:24:55,202 --> 00:24:57,241
