473
00:26:04,542 --> 00:26:05,941
Should I put more of this?

474
00:26:05,942 --> 00:26:08,441
- Yes.
- Okay. I don't know, you do it.

475
00:26:08,442 --> 00:26:10,112
(Welcome)

476
00:26:10,612 --> 00:26:13,311
It's not spicy. Yes.

477
00:26:13,312 --> 00:26:15,182
