478
00:26:15,712 --> 00:26:16,752
Don't worry.

479
00:26:17,752 --> 00:26:18,752
(Don't worry, I'll mix it for you.)

480
00:26:18,753 --> 00:26:20,352
Like so.

481
00:26:21,192 --> 00:26:23,191
(Mixing Monster is giving her all.)

482
00:26:23,192 --> 00:26:24,262
Yes.

483
00:26:25,992 --> 00:26:28,662
Good job. Good job, Yu Ri.

484
00:26:32,232 --> 00:26:34,001
