485
00:26:34,002 --> 00:26:35,472
- Yes.
- Thank you.

486
00:26:35,602 --> 00:26:36,772
Okay.

487
00:26:38,772 --> 00:26:41,342
(Am I eating well?)

488
00:26:41,672 --> 00:26:43,812
