- Yes.

517
00:27:50,942 --> 00:27:52,441
It's really hard, you know.

518
00:27:52,442 --> 00:27:55,451
- It's hard. Yes.
- It's hard.

519
00:27:55,452 --> 00:27:56,452
Okay.

520
00:27:58,182 --> 00:28:00,592
